{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban holiday companies from implementing price hikes during school breaks",
        "additional_details": "We want to make memories with our children that will last a lifetime. Many of us can\u2019t due to the price of holidays. Teachers can also suffer financially for this reason.",
        "background": "We feel that families (be that single parent families, one income families or other less fortunate families) are being squeezed by holiday companies with price increases in the school breaks. We feel this is unfair.",
